messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com

I want deliverance from spiritual blindness and sexual sins I want the holy Spirit to come into my life and destroy the works of the devil I want my will delivered from the will of Satan I come against all spirits of lust and adultery working against my marriage and I want to be delivered from these spirits

We're here to support you in your journey towards healing. Let's pray together for deliverance from spiritual blindness and sexual sins. 

Heavenly Father, we come before you today, asking for your Holy Spirit to fill our lives and destroy the works of the devil. We renounce all spirits of lust and adultery that are working against your marriage. In the name of Jesus Christ, we command these spirits to leave and declare freedom over your life. 

If you would like, I can guide you through specific prayers or resources to help you further. How can I assist you today?
I would love that

Great! Here are some specific prayers you can use for deliverance and healing:

1. **Prayer for Deliverance**: 
   "Lord, I ask for your deliverance from all spirits of lust and adultery. I surrender my will to you and ask that you break every chain that binds me. Fill me with your Holy Spirit and guide me in your truth. Amen."

2. **Prayer for Healing**: 
   "Heavenly Father, I seek your healing touch in my life. Heal my heart and mind from the wounds of sin. Help me to walk in purity and righteousness. I trust in your grace and mercy. Amen."

3. **Prayer for Strength**: 
   "Lord, grant me the strength to resist temptation and to stand firm in my faith. Help me to focus on you and your word, and to seek your guidance in all things. Amen."

If you need more resources or specific scriptures to meditate on, just let me know! We're here to support you every step of the way.
I pray for my marital bed to be cleansed of all sexual impurity I forsake and renounce all sexual sins and I want them washed from my memory

That's a powerful prayer! Here’s a prayer you can use for cleansing your marital bed and renouncing sexual sins:

"Heavenly Father, I come before you today to pray for my marital bed. I ask that you cleanse it of all sexual impurity and fill it with your love and holiness. I forsake and renounce all sexual sins that have affected my marriage. Wash them from my memory and help me to walk in purity and righteousness. I trust in your power to restore and heal. In the name of Jesus Christ, I pray. Amen."

If you would like more support or resources, feel free to ask! We're here for you.
I renounce and forsake all of Satan lies and I release myself from his grips and I release the fire of God to cleanse me of all things that are evil and wicked

That's a strong declaration! Here’s a prayer you can use to renounce Satan's lies and seek God's cleansing:

"Heavenly Father, I renounce and forsake all of Satan's lies. I release myself from his grips and declare that I am free in the name of Jesus Christ. I ask you to send your fire to cleanse me of all things that are evil and wicked. Fill me with your Holy Spirit and guide me in your truth. Thank you for your love and for setting me free. In Jesus' name, I pray. Amen."

If you need further support or guidance, just let me know! We're here to help you on your journey.
I release myself from the spirit of this world I release myself from lust fornication adultery harlotry masturbation perversion homosexuality and all desires to practice immorality

That's a powerful declaration of freedom! Here’s a prayer you can use to release yourself from those spirits and desires:

"Heavenly Father, I release myself from the spirit of this world. I renounce lust, fornication, adultery, harlotry, masturbation, perversion, homosexuality, and all desires to practice immorality. I ask for your cleansing and healing in my life. Fill me with your Holy Spirit and help me to walk in purity and righteousness. Thank you for your grace and for setting me free. In the name of Jesus Christ, I pray. Amen."

If you need more prayers or resources, feel free to reach out! We're here to support you.
Freedom from the stronghold these sins have had in my life over the years and the blindness that Satan has bought through the deception of these sins

It's important to seek freedom from those strongholds and the deception that has come with them. Here’s a prayer you can use for that:

"Heavenly Father, I come before you seeking freedom from the stronghold that these sins have had in my life over the years. I renounce the blindness that Satan has brought through the deception of these sins. I ask for your light to shine in my life, revealing the truth and setting me free. I claim the victory over these strongholds in the name of Jesus Christ. Thank you for your healing and deliverance. Amen."

If you need further support or guidance, please let me know! We're here to help you on your journey towards healing and freedom.

I pray for the restoration of my soul and deliverance from any sexual oppression as a result of these sins I pray for restored joy I want my eyes open to just how evil these sins are in the eyes of God

That's a heartfelt prayer, and it's wonderful that you're seeking restoration and deliverance. Here’s a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I pray for the restoration of my soul and deliverance from any sexual oppression that has resulted from my sins. I ask for your Holy Spirit to open my eyes to the true nature of these sins and how they grieve you. Restore my joy, Lord, and help me to walk in your light. I renounce any lies of the enemy that have kept me in darkness. Thank you for your grace and mercy. In Jesus' name, I pray. Amen."

If you need more resources or support, feel free to reach out! We're here to assist you on your journey.

I release all sexual sin from my life and I want the demonic alter of sexual sins that Satan has built in my life to be destroyed by God and I repent and renounce all sins and agreement and involvement with Satan that would prevent my prayers from being answered

It's powerful that you're taking this step to release those sins and seek God's intervention. Here’s a prayer you can use for this purpose:

"Heavenly Father, I release all sexual sin from my life and ask that you destroy the demonic altar of sexual sins that Satan has built within me. I repent and renounce all sins, agreements, and involvement with Satan that would hinder my prayers from being answered. I claim the authority of Jesus Christ over my life and ask for your cleansing and restoration. Thank you for your forgiveness and for breaking every chain that binds me. In Jesus' name, I pray. Amen."

If you need further support or guidance, please let me know! We're here to help you on your journey towards healing and freedom.
I repent and ask forgiveness for not being a good husband and I ask that any evil influence that keeps me from being a Godly husband would be destroyed by Jesus

It's commendable that you're seeking repentance and forgiveness. Here’s a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I come before you with a humble heart, repenting for not being the husband I should be. I ask for your forgiveness and for the strength to be a Godly husband. I pray that any evil influence that keeps me from fulfilling this role is destroyed by the power of Jesus. Help me to walk in love, patience, and understanding, reflecting your grace in my marriage. Thank you for your mercy and for the transformation you are bringing into my life. In Jesus' name, I pray. Amen."

If you need more support or resources, feel free to reach out! We're here to assist you on your journey.
I renounce the spirit of disobedience and rebellion that causes me to be disobedient to the word of God I repent for living contrary to the word of God while being in the church

It's great that you're taking this step to renounce disobedience and seek repentance. Here’s a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I renounce the spirit of disobedience and rebellion in my life. I repent for living contrary to your Word, especially while being part of the church. I ask for your forgiveness and for the strength to align my life with your teachings. Help me to walk in obedience and to reflect your love and truth in all that I do. Thank you for your grace and for the new beginnings you offer. In Jesus' name, I pray. Amen."

If you need further guidance or support, just let me know! We're here to help you on your journey towards healing and obedience.
I want to represent my body to God as a living sacrifice and I renounce the ways that I have used his body for earthly pleasures

That's a powerful commitment! Here’s a prayer you can use to express your desire to present your body to God as a living sacrifice:

"Heavenly Father, I come before you today to present my body as a living sacrifice, holy and acceptable to You. I renounce the ways I have used this body for earthly pleasures that do not honor You. I ask for your forgiveness and for the strength to live in a way that glorifies You. Help me to seek You earnestly and to find my satisfaction in You alone. Thank you for your grace and for the transformation you bring. In Jesus' name, I pray. Amen."

If you need more support or resources, feel free to ask! We're here to assist you on your journey.
